Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.41,0:01:40.50,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}籠罩了這片土地
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.50,0:01:43.08,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}這是與討伐邪惡的勇者的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.08,0:01:45.50,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}短暫旅途的記憶
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.47,0:01:58.01,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}故事結束
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.01,0:02:00.35,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}勇者沉眠
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.35,0:02:03.06,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}平穩的日常
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.06,0:02:04.90,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}留給這片土地
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.90,0:02:07.11,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}時光流逝如梭
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.11,0:02:09.48,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}帶走人的思念
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.48,0:02:12.20,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}你刻下的道道軌跡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.20,0:02:13.99,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}也漸漸染上鏽斑
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.99,0:02:15.99,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}儘管如此
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.99,0:02:18.20,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}你說過的話 你的願望和勇氣
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.20,0:02:21.50,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}現在也毫無疑問
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.50,0:02:23.66,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}在我心中迴盪
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.25,0:02:25.88,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}踏上同一條旅途
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.88,0:02:27.96,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}明明沒什麼特別的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.96,0:02:29.59,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}卻讓我眼角含淚
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.59,0:02:34.09,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}不知何時起 我變得想要知道
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.09,0:02:35.30,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}這一切的緣由
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.30,0:02:36.26,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}哪怕已經太遲
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.26,0:02:38.76,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}只要再次踏上與你走過的旅程
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.76,0:02:42.18,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}哪怕你已經不在那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.18,0:02:44.27,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}也一定能夠找到
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.09,0:22:51.97,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}And you alright
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.18,0:22:54.85,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}Can you hear me
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.06,0:23:01.65,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}誰もいない線路沿いをなぞってく
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.06,0:23:04.07,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}おおげさに泣いて
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.07,0:23:06.99,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}笑って欲しくて
